    <li>Replace deprecation usage of annotation indexer externalizer</li>
    <li>Imported interfaces @Query(FooInterface::class) are marked as unused when used for constant <a href="https://github.com/Haehnchen/idea-php-annotation-plugin/issues/82">#82</a></li>
</ul>

