<ul>
    <li>PhpStorm 2017.1 build</li>
    <li>Add FOSRest alias <a href="https://github.com/Haehnchen/idea-php-annotation-plugin/issues/87">#87</a> @Koc</li>
</ul>

<h2>4.3.2</h2>
<ul>
    <li>Replace deprecated api usages</li>
</ul>

